ActBoards of Trade Act
SubjectLa Chambre de commerce de Danville (Quebec) ** Change of Boundaries **
PrecisOrder approving the application by the CHAMBRE DE COMMERCE DE DANVILLE, in Quebec, to CHANGE THE BOUNDARIES OF ITS DISTRICT from the municipality of Danville and Shipton to the MRC des Sources, namely the cities of Danville, Asbestos, Wotton, Saint-Georges-de-Windsor, Saint-Camille, Saint-Adrien, and Ham-Sud.
